@SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress = http://localhost:5158
@ContentType = application/json

### Get all tasks
GET {{SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress}}/api/tasks
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### Get task by ID
GET {{SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/1
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### Create a new task
POST {{SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "title": "Complete project documentation",
  "description": "Write comprehensive documentation for the task manager API",
  "priority": 4,
  "dueDate": "2025-08-10T10:00:00Z"
}

###

### Create another task
POST {{SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "title": "Review code",
  "description": "Review the implementation and test all endpoints",
  "priority": 3,
  "dueDate": "2025-08-08T15:30:00Z"
}

###

### Create a simple task
POST {{SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "title": "Buy groceries",
  "priority": 2
}

###

### Create an overdue task for testing
POST {{SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "title": "Overdue task",
  "description": "This task is already overdue",
  "priority": 5,
  "dueDate": "2025-08-01T10:00:00Z"
}

###

### Update a task
PUT {{SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "title": "Complete project documentation - UPDATED",
  "description": "Write comprehensive documentation for the task manager API with examples",
  "isComplete": false,
  "priority": 5,
  "dueDate": "2025-08-09T10:00:00Z"
}

###

### Mark task as complete
PATCH {{SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/1/complete
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### Get completed tasks
GET {{SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/status/true
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### Get pending tasks
GET {{SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/status/false
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### Get high priority tasks (priority 4)
GET {{SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/priority/4
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### Get critical priority tasks (priority 5)
GET {{SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/priority/5
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### Get overdue tasks
GET {{SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/overdue
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### Get task statistics
GET {{SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/statistics
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

### Delete a task
DELETE {{SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/3

###

### Test error handling - Get non-existent task
GET {{SimpleTaskManager_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/999
Accept: {{ContentType}}

###

